qStateName.desc:
Name of the alternate state.
Default is current selections $.

qSize.desc: Defines the size of a list object.

qError.desc: This parameter is optional and is displayed in case of error.

qExpressions.desc: Lists the expressions in the list object.

qDataPages.desc:
Set of data.
Is empty if nothing has been defined in qInitialDataFetch in ListObjectDef.
